731592f-b.title: Feast of Maria Santissima del Soccoroso.
731592f-b.text:
(1)
Altar to "Maria Santissima del Soccoroso" during her Fiesta on
Elizabeth Street, south of Grand Street.
August 14, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.

(2)
Elizabeth Street, north from Hester to Grand Streets, decorated for the Feast of Maria Santissima del Soccoroso.
August 14, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
731592f-b.folder: Elizabeth Street and Grand Street, Manhattan, N.Y.
